---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Abhinav Kayastha - RF Software Engineer at Nokia"
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<style>
		@keyframes slideInLeft {
			from {
				opacity: 0;
				transform: translateX(-20px);
			}
			to {
				opacity: 1;
				transform: translateX(0);
			}
		}

		@keyframes fadeIn {
			from {
				opacity: 0;
			}
			to {
				opacity: 1;
			}
		}

		h2 {
			position: relative;
			padding-bottom: 0.5em;
			margin-top: 2em;
			margin-bottom: 1em;
			animation: slideInLeft 0.6s ease-out;
		}

		h2::after {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			bottom: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 100%;
			height: 3px;
			background: linear-gradient(90deg, #58a6ff 0%, #79c0ff 50%, transparent 100%);
		}

		h2:first-of-type::after {
			display: none;
		}

		p {
			animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
			line-height: 1.8;
		}

		.achievement-item {
			padding: 1.2em 0 1.2em 1.5em;
			position: relative;
			border-left: 3px solid #58a6ff;
			margin: 1em 0;
			animation: slideInLeft 0.6s ease-out;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
		}

		.achievement-item:hover {
			border-left-color: #79c0ff;
			padding-left: 2em;
		}

		.achievement-item strong {
			color: #79c0ff;
		}

		ul {
			list-style: none;
			padding: 0;
		}

		ul li {
			padding: 0.5em 0 0.5em 1.5em;
			position: relative;
			animation: slideInLeft 0.6s ease-out;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
		}

		ul li:before {
			content: '▸';
			position: absolute;
			left: 0;
			color: #58a6ff;
			font-size: 1.2em;
		}

		ul li:hover {
			color: #79c0ff;
			padding-left: 2em;
		}

		.tech-display {
			margin: 1.5em 0;
			animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
		}

		.tech-display strong {
			display: block;
			color: #79c0ff;
			margin-bottom: 0.5em;
		}

		.language-item {
			display: inline-block;
			margin-right: 2em;
			margin-bottom: 0.5em;
			animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
		}

		.language-item strong {
			color: #58a6ff;
		}
	</style>

	<h2>Professional Background</h2>
	<p>
		I'm a Maintenance Engineer at Nokia working in Oulu, Finland, specializing in RF Software development. 
		With a strong foundation in embedded systems, CI/CD automation, and full-stack web development, I'm 
		passionate about building robust, scalable solutions for complex technical challenges.
	</p>

	<h2>Current Focus</h2>
	<p>
		At Nokia, I focus on:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Creating monitoring scripts for base transceiver stations (BTS)</li>
		<li>Developing tailormade applications for telecom operators worldwide</li>
		<li>Maintaining and improving CI/CD pipeline infrastructure</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Education</h2>
	<p>
		<strong>🎓 Bachelor of Engineering, Information Technology (IoT – Embedded Devices)</strong><br />
		Metropolia University of Applied Sciences | August 2022 – May 2025<br />
		<em>Graduated a year early. Degree was 4 years but finished in 3.</em>
	</p>
	<p>
		<strong>📚 Highschool Diploma, IB: International Baccalaureate</strong><br />
		Kuopion Lyseon lukio | August 2019 – June 2022
	</p>

	<h2>Key Achievements</h2>
	<div class="achievement-item">
		<strong>🚀 Nokia PIM Detection Project</strong><br />
		Developed a full-stack web application for data visualization of network interference in 4G & 5G, enabling engineers to identify PIM related issues <strong>99.95% faster</strong>
	</div>

	<div class="achievement-item">
		<strong>🏆 Best Paper Award</strong><br />
		"YOLO for Urban Traffic: Insights from Helsinki Port Surveillance" - Ranked <strong>#1 out of 387 papers</strong> at SoCTA2024
	</div>

	<div class="achievement-item">
		<strong>🤖 Computer Vision Research</strong><br />
		Achieved <strong>96% accuracy</strong> in human and vehicle detection models during internship at University of Turku
	</div>

	<h2>Technical Expertise</h2>
	<div class="tech-display">
		<strong>Languages</strong>
		Python, Bash, C, C++, Robot Framework, JavaScript, SQL
	</div>
	<div class="tech-display">
		<strong>Technologies</strong>
		Flask, Docker, Jenkins, Yocto, GitLab CI
	</div>
	<div class="tech-display">
		<strong>Tools</strong>
		Git, Linux, CI/CD Pipelines, GitHub Copilot, MQTT
	</div>
	<div class="tech-display">
		<strong>Specializations</strong>
		Embedded systems, RF software, IoT, full-stack web development
	</div>

	<h2>Languages</h2>
	<div style="margin: 1.5em 0;">
		<div class="language-item">
			<strong>Native:</strong> English, Maithili, Nepali
		</div>
		<div class="language-item">
			<strong>Conversational:</strong> Finnish
		</div>
		<div class="language-item">
			<strong>Basic:</strong> Swedish
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2>Notable Projects</h2>
	<div class="achievement-item">
		<strong>🐦 Smart Bird Feeder</strong> (October 2024 – March 2025)<br />
		IoT Smart Bird Feeder using Node.js, Express.js, MQTT & WebSockets for real-time monitoring. Developed a responsive web dashboard with real-time data, historical tracking, and CSV export functionality.
	</div>

	<div class="achievement-item">
		<strong>☁️ Personal Cloud Infrastructure</strong> (July 2025)<br />
		Self-hosted private cloud on Raspberry Pi 4 using Nextcloud AIO, Docker & Portainer with Cloudflare Tunnel, firewall rules & SSL for secure remote access.
	</div>

	<div class="achievement-item">
		<strong>🐧 Embedded Linux Development</strong> (October 2024 – December 2024)<br />
		Built and optimized embedded Linux development workflow with Yocto Project for ARM-based systems, supporting cross-compilation and automated builds.
	</div>
</Layout>
